{"tid":406247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查指全球約4000萬人屬「現代奴隸」","createTime":"2017-09-19T13:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T13:36:17.000Z","uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb9023ebfb8c4a08b0d97c792b4ffd76aa42622a","tid":406247,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有組織調查指出，全球有約四千萬人屬於「現代奴隸」。<br />\n<br />\n國際勞工組織和行走自由基金會等機構，在近五十個國家進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n得出的數據反映，去年有多達四千萬人淪為現代奴隸制度的受害者，其中近二千五百萬人被迫在工廠、地盤或漁船工作，部分更被迫從事性工作，另外有約一千五百萬人被迫出嫁。<br />\n<br />\n數據指，「現代奴隸」中大部分來自非洲和亞洲國家，約四分之三是女性。<br />\n<br />\n國際勞工組織另一份報告亦指出，逾1.52億兒童淪為童工，呼籲國際社會關注問題，並促請各國政府保障勞工權益，同時加強打擊非法移民問題。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=236560&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D236560%26refer%3Dshare&d=RwxKApIyLqjTLCqDI3HY%2Bv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=942c7170\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D236560%26refer%3Dshare&h=c315c131\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=236560&amp;refer=share</a>"},{"pid":"aeedfad1d55ee82d9c2b696fe6aaf642c8e6a0f2","tid":406247,"uid":39245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"非正式統計， 香港佔其中700萬"},{"pid":"8e78b60dec7023cec22c1fa86937f1d7014f900c","tid":406247,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f4473dc2fc84f1658e074d419327a40626a571","tid":406247,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}